{"article_id":"6Hu1e8OqgibPcgXN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"We all know the terrible answers .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"Had Mr. Arbery not been black ,","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"it would not have taken law enforcement authorities in Georgia more than two months to be shamed into seeking some semblance of justice in his killing .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"The announcement by a Georgia prosecutor","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that the case would be presented to a grand jury for consideration of criminal charges against the two men","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"involved in the shooting","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"came Tuesday , the same day","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that a video of the Feb. 23 shooting surfaced ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"sparking outrage","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"and reigniting America ' s debate","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"about whether black lives matter .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"The arrest of the two men came two days later .","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"The 36-second video is difficult to watch .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Taken from inside a vehicle ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"it shows the unarmed , 25-year-old Mr. Arbery jogging on a residential road","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"when he comes upon a white truck","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"stopped in the street .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"One white man is standing in the bed of the pickup and another beside its open driver ' s-side door .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Both are armed , one with a shotgun .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Mr. Arbery runs around the truck","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and disappears from view","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"before he reemerges .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"There is muffled shouting","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"and three shots sound","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"as Mr. Arbery tussles with the man with the shotgun","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"before he stumbles","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"and falls on the road .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"There is blood on his shirt .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"The two men are father and son .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The father , Gregory McMichael , is a former police officer and retired investigator in the local district attorney ' s office","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"who told police","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"he and his son chased Mr. Arbery","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"because he resembled a suspect in a rash of recent break-ins .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"The video appears to contradict portions of that account ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"and the handling of the case doesn ' t inspire confidence .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Police apparently limited their investigation to interviewing Mr. McMichael ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"while a prosecutor concluded","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"that the men had acted legally under Georgia ' s citizen arrest and self-defense statutes .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Authorities obtained a video of the incident","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"but refused to share it with Mr. Arbery ' s family .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"They seemed more upset","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that the video","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"that appeared on the Internet","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"had been posted","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"than with its gut-wrenching contents .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The arrest of the father and son came after the outcry","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"caused by the release of the video and the intervention of state officials .","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"\" All","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"I want to do","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"is get justice for my son , \"","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"said Marcus Arbery , the slain man ' s father .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"\" This is terrible .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"It could happen to anybody ' s kid. \"","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"We would add :","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"especially , and tragically ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"if they are black .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":111,"left":58,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":0,"right":57,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":57,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":110,"left":99,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":66,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":65,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":65,"left":60,"right":64,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":60,"left":3,"right":59,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":61,"right":63,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":8,"right":62,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":62,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":91,"right":97,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":91,"left":12,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":80,"right":89,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":71,"right":79,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":69,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":13,"right":68,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":68,"left":14,"right":67,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":73,"right":78,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":73,"left":19,"right":72,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":27,"relation":"joint","nuclear